[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Bug Tracker — System Overview
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] A Next.js 16 SaaS application for teams to capture, triage, and manage software issues inside authenticated multi-tenant workspaces.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Architecture at a Glance
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] Browser (Next.js App Router)
[CLAUDE]   └── Authenticated Routes  (/app/(authenticated)/*)
[CLAUDE]   └── Public Routes         (/login, /signup, /invitations/*)
[CLAUDE]   └── API Routes            (/app/api/*)
[CLAUDE]        ├── /auth/*          — session, login, signup, password flows
[CLAUDE]        ├── /bugs/*          — CRUD, comments, attachments, history
[CLAUDE]        ├── /agent/*         — machine-to-machine bug operations
[CLAUDE]        ├── /extension/*     — Chrome extension API surface
[CLAUDE]        ├── /admin/*         — platform admin (projects, users, monitoring)
[CLAUDE]        └── /organizations/* — org membership and invitations
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] PostgreSQL (primary store)
[CLAUDE]   └── Managed via postgres-worker.ts (Worker thread)
[CLAUDE]   └── In-memory SQLite for fast unit tests
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Major Subsystems
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Subsystem | Location | Purpose |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|---|
[CLAUDE] | Auth | `src/lib/auth/` | Session, registration, password, email verification |
[CLAUDE] | Bugs | `src/lib/bugs/` | Bug CRUD, comments, attachments, history, import/export |
[CLAUDE] | Organizations | `src/lib/organizations/` | Multi-tenancy, membership, invitations, billing |
[CLAUDE] | Projects | `src/lib/projects/` | Project + section management |
[CLAUDE] | Monitoring | `src/lib/monitoring/` | Observability, alerts, error grouping, performance |
[CLAUDE] | Notifications | `src/lib/notifications/` | Email dispatch via SendGrid |
[CLAUDE] | Extension | `src/lib/extension/` | Chrome extension auth and version management |
[CLAUDE] | Agent | `src/lib/bugs/agent-*.ts` | Automated/AI bug intake and operations |
[CLAUDE] | Settings | `src/lib/settings/` | API keys, JWT auth, API access config |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Key Technology Choices
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - **Framework**: Next.js 16 with App Router (webpack bundler)
[CLAUDE] - **Language**: TypeScript 5
[CLAUDE] - **Database**: PostgreSQL (primary), in-memory SQLite (tests)
[CLAUDE] - **UI**: React 19, shadcn/ui, Tailwind CSS 4
[CLAUDE] - **Email**: SendGrid
[CLAUDE] - **Validation**: Zod 4
[CLAUDE] - **AI/Agent Integration**: MCP (Model Context Protocol) server
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Entry Points
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - **Web app**: `http://localhost:3000`
[CLAUDE] - **Dev server**: `npm run dev`
[CLAUDE] - **MCP server**: `npm run mcp:server`
[CLAUDE] - **Bug agent CLI**: `npm run bugs:cli`
[CLAUDE] - **Alerts CLI**: `npm run alerts:cli`
[CLAUDE] 
