[CLAUDE] ---
[CLAUDE] type: system
[CLAUDE] owner: engineering
[CLAUDE] last_updated: 2026-04-20
[CLAUDE] source_count: 10
[CLAUDE] tags: [notifications, email, sendgrid, templates]
[CLAUDE] status: active
[CLAUDE] ---
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Notification System
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Architecture
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] Bug / Auth event
[CLAUDE]     → BugNotificationEventService   (decides whether to fire)
[CLAUDE]     → BugRecipientService           (resolves recipient list)
[CLAUDE]     → NotificationDispatcher        (routes to delivery channel)
[CLAUDE]     → SendGridDelivery              (delivers via SendGrid API)
[CLAUDE]     → NotificationStore             (persists delivery record)
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Event Types
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Events that trigger notifications (inferred from email templates):
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Template | Trigger |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | `bug-created.html` | New bug filed |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-assigned.html` | Bug assigned to user |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-status-changed.html` | Bug status updated |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-closed.html` | Bug closed |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-reopened.html` | Bug reopened |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-comment.html` | Comment added |
[CLAUDE] | `organization-invitation.html` | User invited to org |
[CLAUDE] | `verification.html` | Email verification required |
[CLAUDE] | `welcome.html` | Signup complete |
[CLAUDE] | `forgot-password.html` | Password reset requested |
[CLAUDE] | `password-changed.html` | Password changed |
[CLAUDE] | `password-reset-complete.html` | Password reset completed |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Template Engine
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `template-engine.ts` compiles HTML templates from `src/lib/notifications/templates/` using a base layout (`base-layout.html`) that all transactional emails extend.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `email-template-registry.ts` maps event types to templates and required variables.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Settings
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Notification settings (which recipient groups receive which events) are configurable per-organisation via:
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/notifications/settings`
[CLAUDE] - `PATCH /api/admin/notifications/settings`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Service: `notification-admin-service.ts`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Delivery History & Retry
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/notifications/deliveries` — paginated delivery log
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/notifications/deliveries/:id/retry` — retry a failed delivery
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/notifications/events/:id/retry` — replay a notification event
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Local Development
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Leave SendGrid environment variables empty for local development. Email delivery is skipped; notification records are still written to the database.
[CLAUDE] === END FILE ===
[CLAUDE] 
