[CLAUDE] ---
[CLAUDE] type: system
[CLAUDE] owner: engineering
[CLAUDE] last_updated: 2026-04-20
[CLAUDE] source_count: 6
[CLAUDE] tags: [import, export, jobs, data-management]
[CLAUDE] status: active
[CLAUDE] ---
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Bug Data Import / Export
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Overview
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] The admin bug-data panel (`app/(authenticated)/admin/bug-data/`) allows bulk import and export of bug data via asynchronous jobs.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Job Model
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `BugDataManagementJob` fields:
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Field | Description |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | `jobType` | `"import"` or `"export"` |
[CLAUDE] | `status` | `queued → running → completed / completed_with_warnings / failed` |
[CLAUDE] | `sourceFileName` | Input file for imports |
[CLAUDE] | `resultFilePath` | Output archive for exports |
[CLAUDE] | `summary` | JSON object with counts (bugCount, historyEntryCount, attachmentCount, missingFileCount) |
[CLAUDE] | `warnings` / `errors` | Per-job issue lists |
[CLAUDE] | `downloadUrl` | Presigned URL for export download (populated after completion) |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Import Flow
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] 1. Upload CSV → validation pass (`bug-data-import-service.ts`) returns `BugImportValidationResult`
[CLAUDE]    - per-row validation with field-level issues
[CLAUDE] 2. User confirms → execution pass returns `BugImportExecutionResult`
[CLAUDE]    - `duplicateStrategy`: `skip_existing` or `update_existing`
[CLAUDE]    - summary: `createdCount`, `updatedCount`, `skippedCount`, `failedCount`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Export Flow
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] 1. Admin triggers export → job queued
[CLAUDE] 2. Worker processes bugs, history, and attachments into an archive
[CLAUDE] 3. `BugExportManifestSummary` is stored in job summary
[CLAUDE] 4. Download URL made available on job completion
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Job Store
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `bug-data-job-store.ts` persists job records. `bug-data-admin-service.ts` exposes admin-level operations.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Helper Utilities (`bug-data-management-panel.helpers.ts`)
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - `summarizeBugDataJobs(jobs)` — counts by status, identifies latest import/export
[CLAUDE] - `formatBugDataJobSummary(job)` — human-readable summary string
[CLAUDE] - `formatBugImportValidationSummary(validation)` — total/valid/invalid row counts
[CLAUDE] - `getBugImportRowsWithIssues(validation)` — rows with validation failures
[CLAUDE] - `formatBugImportExecutionSummary(summary)` — created/updated/skipped/failed counts
[CLAUDE] - `getBugDataJobIssueMessages(job)` — merged error + warning message list
[CLAUDE] === END FILE ===
[CLAUDE] 
