[CLAUDE] ---
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Local Development Setup
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Prerequisites
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - Node.js + npm
[CLAUDE] - Docker + Docker Compose
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## First-Time Setup
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```bash
[CLAUDE] # 1. Clone and enter the repo
[CLAUDE] cd /path/to/bug_tracker
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # 2. Create local env file
[CLAUDE] cp .env.example .env
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # 3. Install dependencies
[CLAUDE] npm install
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # 4. Start PostgreSQL
[CLAUDE] docker compose up -d postgres
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # 5. Apply database migrations
[CLAUDE] npm run db:migrate:postgres
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # 6. Start the dev server
[CLAUDE] npm run dev
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Open http://localhost:3000.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Daily Workflow
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Task | Command |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | Start dev server | `npm run dev` |
[CLAUDE] | Run fast unit tests | `npm run test` |
[CLAUDE] | Run PostgreSQL unit tests | `npm run test:unit:postgres` |
[CLAUDE] | Type-check | `npm run typecheck` |
[CLAUDE] | Lint | `npm run lint` |
[CLAUDE] | Production build | `npm run build && npm run start` |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## E2E Tests
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```bash
[CLAUDE] # Seed test DB and start on port 3001
[CLAUDE] npm run dev:playwright
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # In another terminal
[CLAUDE] npm run test:e2e
[CLAUDE] npm run test:e2e:ui    # with Playwright UI
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Agent / CLI Tools
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```bash
[CLAUDE] npm run bugs:cli      # bug agent CLI
[CLAUDE] npm run alerts:cli    # operational alerts CLI
[CLAUDE] npm run mcp:server    # MCP tool server for LLM agents
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Environment Variables
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Key variables in `.env`:
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Variable | Purpose |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | `DATABASE_URL` | PostgreSQL connection string |
[CLAUDE] | `SENDGRID_API_KEY` | Email delivery (optional for local dev) |
[CLAUDE] | `BUG_TRACKER_TEST_DB_BACKEND` | `memory` (default) or `postgres` for tests |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Troubleshooting
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - **`db:migrate:postgres` fails** — check Docker is running: `docker compose ps`
[CLAUDE] - **Port 5432 in use** — stop local PostgreSQL: `brew services stop postgresql` or equivalent
[CLAUDE] - **Type errors after pull** — run `npm run typecheck` to regenerate Next.js types
[CLAUDE] === END FILE ===
[CLAUDE] 
