[CLAUDE] # Incomplete Helper Implementations
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Summary
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Several helper/utility files have structural scaffolding in place but contain empty or stub implementations inside switch/case blocks and return statements. These were identified in the source snapshot as of 2026-04-20.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Affected Files
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### `bug-data-management-panel.helpers.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - `summarizeBugDataJobs`: `reduce` accumulator body is empty; `return {}` at the end returns an empty object instead of counts-by-status map.
[CLAUDE] - `formatBugDataJobProgress` (import branch): empty return.
[CLAUDE] - `formatBugDataJobIssueSummary` (error/warning branches): empty returns — always falls through to `"No issues"` even when issues exist.
[CLAUDE] - `formatBugDataJobSummary` (import branch): empty return.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### `bug-history.helpers.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - `formatBugHistoryEventLabel`: entire `switch` body empty — returns `undefined` for all event types.
[CLAUDE] - `getBugHistoryEntrySource` (import branch, bug branch): empty returns.
[CLAUDE] - `formatBugHistoryChange` (set/cleared/unchanged branches): empty returns.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### `all-bugs-filters.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - Multiple normalizer functions (`normalizeOptionalPositiveInteger`, `normalizeOptionalDate`, `normalizeSortField`, `normalizeSortDirection`) have empty early-return and error branches.
[CLAUDE] - `parseAllBugFilters`: entire function body is empty (returns `{}` cast to `AllBugsFilterState`).
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### `alert-list-filters.ts` / `notification-center-filters.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - Filter builders have empty `if` branches — search params may not be appended correctly.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Risk
[CLAUDE] 
