[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Bug Tracker — System Overview
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] A Next.js 16 application for teams to capture, triage, and manage software issues inside an authenticated workspace.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Tech Stack
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Layer | Technology |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | Framework | Next.js 16.1.6 (App Router, webpack mode) |
[CLAUDE] | Language | TypeScript 5 |
[CLAUDE] | UI | React 19, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui |
[CLAUDE] | Database | PostgreSQL (primary), in-memory SQLite (tests) |
[CLAUDE] | Email | SendGrid |
[CLAUDE] | Runtime | Node.js |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Major Subsystems
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Subsystem | Location | Purpose |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|---|
[CLAUDE] | Auth | `src/lib/auth/` | Login, signup, sessions, password flows |
[CLAUDE] | Bugs | `src/lib/bugs/` | Core bug CRUD, comments, attachments, history |
[CLAUDE] | Organizations | `src/lib/organizations/` | Multi-tenant orgs, membership, invitations, billing |
[CLAUDE] | Projects | `src/lib/projects/` | Project + section management |
[CLAUDE] | Monitoring | `src/lib/monitoring/` | Operational logs, alerts, error fingerprinting, performance |
[CLAUDE] | Notifications | `src/lib/notifications/` | Email dispatch via SendGrid, templates, delivery tracking |
[CLAUDE] | Agent API | `src/app/api/agent/` | Programmatic bug operations for automated agents |
[CLAUDE] | Extension API | `src/app/api/extension/` | Chrome extension auth and bug reporting |
[CLAUDE] | Admin API | `src/app/api/admin/` | Admin-only management surfaces |
[CLAUDE] | Settings | `src/lib/settings/` | API keys, JWT config, API access |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## URL Structure
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] /                        → redirect
[CLAUDE] /login                   → login form
[CLAUDE] /signup                  → registration + org creation
[CLAUDE] /dashboard               → authenticated home
[CLAUDE] /bugs                    → bug list with filters
[CLAUDE] /bugs/[bugId]            → bug detail
[CLAUDE] /bugs/new                → create bug
[CLAUDE] /admin/*                 → admin panel
[CLAUDE] /settings/*              → user/org settings
[CLAUDE] /organization/*          → org management
[CLAUDE] /billing                 → billing panel
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## API Route Groups
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - `/api/auth/*` — authentication flows
[CLAUDE] - `/api/bugs/*` — bug CRUD and sub-resources
[CLAUDE] - `/api/agent/bugs/*` — agent-facing bug API
[CLAUDE] - `/api/extension/*` — Chrome extension API
[CLAUDE] - `/api/admin/*` — admin operations
[CLAUDE] - `/api/organizations/*` — org management
[CLAUDE] - `/api/projects/*` — project management
[CLAUDE] - `/api/invitations/*` — invitation flows
[CLAUDE] - `/api/observability/*` — client-side telemetry ingestion
[CLAUDE] - `/api/settings/*` — API key and access settings
[CLAUDE] 
