[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Monitoring & Observability
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Request Observability
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] All API routes are wrapped with `withRequestObservability("METHOD", handler)` from `src/lib/monitoring/request-observability.ts`. This middleware logs structured request/response events.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Operational Logs
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/operational-log-service.ts` + `operational-log-store.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Severity levels: `debug`, `info`, `warn`, `error`, `critical`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Admin endpoint: `GET /api/admin/logs` — paginated log query with severity filter.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Error Grouping
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/grouped-errors-service.ts` — groups `error` and `critical` log entries by fingerprint.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/error-fingerprint.ts` — fingerprint algorithm for deduplication.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Admin endpoint: `GET /api/admin/errors` — returns grouped error clusters with entry detail.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `PATCH /api/admin/errors/[fingerprint]/bug` — links a grouped error to a bug (sets `projectId`).
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Operational Alerts
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/operational-alert-service.ts` + `operational-alert-store.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Alerts have `severity`, `status`, `source`, `latestSeen` timestamp.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Alert filter state (`alert-list-filters.ts`): `severity`, `status`, `source`, `latestSeenFrom`, `latestSeenTo`, `limit`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Admin endpoints:
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/alerts` — list alerts with filters
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/alerts/[alertId]` — alert detail
[CLAUDE] - `PATCH /api/admin/alerts/[alertId]` — update alert status
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/alerts/[alertId]/bugs` — create bug from alert via `createBugFromOperationalAlert()`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Alert CLI: `npm run alerts:cli` → `scripts/alerts-cli.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Performance Monitoring
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/endpoint-performance-service.ts` — tracks per-endpoint latency.  
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/performance.ts` — performance measurement utilities.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Admin endpoints:
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/performance/endpoints?window=...` — endpoint latency aggregates
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/performance/org-usage` — per-org usage stats from `org-usage-service.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Page Load Observability
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/page-load-observability.ts` + `src/components/app/page-load-observability.tsx`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Client sends timing data to `POST /api/observability/page-load`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## File Sink
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/observability-file-sink.ts` — writes NDJSON to `log/observability.ndjson`.  
[CLAUDE] See [observability runbook](../../../runbooks/bug_tracker-observability.md) for details.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Redaction
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `src/lib/monitoring/observability-redaction.ts` — strips sensitive fields before logging.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Dashboard Summary
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `GET /api/admin/dashboard/summary` → `getDashboardSummary()` — aggregated admin home stats.
[CLAUDE] === END FILE ===
[CLAUDE] 
