[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Email Notification System
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Architecture
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] BugNotificationEventService
[CLAUDE]     → BugRecipientService (who gets the email)
[CLAUDE]     → NotificationDispatcher
[CLAUDE]         → SendGridDelivery (actual send)
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] All delivery attempts recorded in `notification-store.ts`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Event Types
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Defined in `bug-notification-event-service.ts`. Known template files:
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Template | Trigger |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | `bug-created.html` | New bug submitted |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-assigned.html` | Bug assigned to user |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-status-changed.html` | Status update |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-closed.html` | Bug closed |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-reopened.html` | Bug reopened |
[CLAUDE] | `bug-comment.html` | New comment |
[CLAUDE] | `forgot-password.html` | Password reset request |
[CLAUDE] | `verification.html` | Email verification |
[CLAUDE] | `welcome.html` | Signup complete |
[CLAUDE] | `organization-invitation.html` | Org invitation sent |
[CLAUDE] | `password-changed.html` | Password changed confirmation |
[CLAUDE] | `password-reset-complete.html` | Reset complete |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Templates extend `base-layout.html`. Rendered by `template-engine.ts`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Template Registry
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `email-template-registry.ts` maps event type strings to template files. `email-template-registry.test.ts` validates all templates compile.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Delivery & Retry
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `notification-admin-service.ts` exposes admin operations:
[CLAUDE] - `listNotificationDeliveryHistory()` — filtered delivery log
[CLAUDE] - `retryNotificationDeliveryForAdmin(deliveryId)` — re-attempt a failed delivery
[CLAUDE] - `retryNotificationEvent(eventId)` — re-dispatch an event
[CLAUDE] - `listNotificationSettingsSummary()` / `updateNotificationSettings()` — per event-type + recipient-group toggles
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Admin endpoints:
[CLAUDE] - `GET/PATCH /api/admin/notifications/settings`
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/notifications/deliveries`
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/notifications/deliveries/[id]/retry`
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/notifications/events/[id]/retry`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Notification Filter State (`notification-center-filters.ts`)
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Fields: `eventType`, `deliveryStatus`, `recipientEmail`, `limit` (default 25).
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## SendGrid Config
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `SENDGRID_API_KEY` env var. Leave empty for local dev (email disabled). Set to enable delivery.
[CLAUDE] === END FILE ===
