[CLAUDE] ---
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Agent API
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] The agent API provides a programmatic interface for automated agents to operate on bugs without a browser session.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Authentication
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `requireAgentApiUser(request)` — agents authenticate via a separate mechanism from browser sessions (see `agent-api.ts`). Errors are returned as structured JSON via `createAgentApiErrorResponse()`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Endpoints
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Method | Route | Purpose |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|---|
[CLAUDE] | GET | `/api/agent/bugs` | List claimable bugs |
[CLAUDE] | GET | `/api/agent/bugs/[bugId]` | Get bug detail |
[CLAUDE] | POST | `/api/agent/bugs/[bugId]/claim` | Claim a bug (`claimedBy: string`) |
[CLAUDE] | PATCH | `/api/agent/bugs/[bugId]/status` | Update agent work state |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### Claim Request
[CLAUDE] ```json
[CLAUDE] { "claimedBy": "agent-name" }
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### Status Update Request
[CLAUDE] ```json
[CLAUDE] {
[CLAUDE]   "claimedBy": "agent-name",
[CLAUDE]   "state": "...",
[CLAUDE]   "statusNote": "optional note"
[CLAUDE] }
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Agent CLI
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `npm run bugs:cli` → `scripts/bug-agent-cli.ts` (wraps `src/lib/bugs/agent-cli.ts`)
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `agent-integration.ts` — higher-level integration helpers.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## MCP Server
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] `npm run mcp:server` → `scripts/mcp-server.ts` → `src/lib/bugs/mcp-server.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Exposes bug tracker operations as MCP tools for Claude and other LLM agents via the `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Design Intent (from product roadmap)
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] The agent layer is designed to support multiple specialised agents:
[CLAUDE] - **Intake agent** — structures incoming reports
[CLAUDE] - **Triage agent** — prioritises and routes
[CLAUDE] - **Investigation agent** — correlates logs, releases, code changes
[CLAUDE] - **QA agent** — suggests verification steps
[CLAUDE] - **Release agent** — checks fix safety
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] See [Agent Architecture concept](../../../concepts/bug_tracker-agent-architecture.md) for the full vision.
[CLAUDE] === END FILE ===
[CLAUDE] 
