[CLAUDE] npm run typecheck           # TypeScript type checking
[CLAUDE] npm run lint                # ESLint
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## E2E Tests
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```bash
[CLAUDE] npm run dev:playwright      # seed test DB + start on port 3001
[CLAUDE] npm run test:e2e            # run Playwright tests
[CLAUDE] npm run test:e2e:ui         # Playwright UI mode
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Build & Production Preview
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```bash
[CLAUDE] npm run build
[CLAUDE] npm run start
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Useful Scripts
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```bash
[CLAUDE] npm run bugs:cli    # bug agent CLI (tsx scripts/bug-agent-cli.ts)
[CLAUDE] npm run alerts:cli  # alerts CLI (tsx scripts/alerts-cli.ts)
