[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Bug Tracker — System Overview
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] A Next.js 16 full-stack application for authenticated teams to capture, triage, and manage software issues. Supports multi-tenant organizations, project-level access control, AI agent integration, a Chrome extension, and an MCP server interface.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## High-Level Architecture
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] Browser (React/Next.js)
[CLAUDE]     │
[CLAUDE]     ├── App Router pages  (/app/(authenticated)/...)
[CLAUDE]     │       └── Client components, server components, filter logic
[CLAUDE]     │
[CLAUDE]     └── API Routes  (/app/api/...)
[CLAUDE]             ├── /auth/*          — session auth, signup, password flows
[CLAUDE]             ├── /bugs/*          — CRUD, comments, attachments, history
[CLAUDE]             ├── /organizations/* — multi-tenant org management
[CLAUDE]             ├── /projects/*      — project + section management
[CLAUDE]             ├── /invitations/*   — org invite flows
[CLAUDE]             ├── /settings/*      — API keys, JWT, access config
[CLAUDE]             ├── /extension/*     — Chrome extension auth + bug submit
[CLAUDE]             ├── /agent/*         — agent API (claim, update, list bugs)
[CLAUDE]             └── /admin/*         — admin-only: users, monitoring, alerts, notifications
[CLAUDE] ```
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Core Layers
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Layer | Path | Responsibility |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|---|
[CLAUDE] | Pages / UI | `src/app/(authenticated)/` | Route segments, React panels, client-side filter state |
[CLAUDE] | API Routes | `src/app/api/` | HTTP handlers, request validation, response shaping |
[CLAUDE] | Services | `src/lib/*/\*-service.ts` | Business logic, orchestration |
[CLAUDE] | Stores | `src/lib/*/\*-store.ts` | Database queries, data access |
[CLAUDE] | DB Client | `src/lib/db/` | PostgreSQL + in-memory adapters, migrations, schema |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Key Subsystems
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - [Auth](./auth.md) — session cookies, email verification, password reset, JWT
[CLAUDE] - [Bugs](./bugs.md) — bug lifecycle, comments, attachments, history, bulk ops, import/export
[CLAUDE] - [Organizations & Projects](./organizations.md) — multi-tenancy, invitations, billing seats
[CLAUDE] - [Notifications](./notifications.md) — SendGrid email dispatch with templates
[CLAUDE] - [Monitoring](./monitoring.md) — operational logs, error grouping, alerts, performance
[CLAUDE] - [Agent Integration](./agent-integration.md) — agent API, CLI, MCP server, coordination notes
[CLAUDE] - [Chrome Extension](./chrome-extension.md) — header-auth extension API, evidence upload
[CLAUDE] - [Admin Panel](./admin.md) — admin surfaces for all above subsystems
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Tech Stack
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] - **Runtime**: Node.js, Next.js 16 (App Router, webpack mode)
[CLAUDE] - **Language**: TypeScript 5
[CLAUDE] - **Database**: PostgreSQL (production), in-memory (unit tests)
[CLAUDE] - **UI**: React 19, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui, Radix primitives
[CLAUDE] - **Email**: SendGrid
[CLAUDE] - **AI/Agent**: MCP SDK (`@modelcontextprotocol/sdk`), custom agent CLI
[CLAUDE] - **Validation**: Runtime type guards (no schema library in API routes)
[CLAUDE] - **Testing**: Node built-in test runner; Playwright for E2E
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Entry Points
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] | Purpose | Command |
[CLAUDE] |---|---|
[CLAUDE] | Dev server | `npm run dev` |
[CLAUDE] | Production build | `npm run build` |
[CLAUDE] | DB migrations | `npm run db:migrate:postgres` |
[CLAUDE] | Unit tests (in-memory) | `npm run test` |
[CLAUDE] | Unit tests (postgres) | `npm run test:unit:postgres` |
[CLAUDE] | E2E tests | `npm run test:e2e` |
[CLAUDE] | Agent CLI | `npm run bugs:cli` |
[CLAUDE] | Alerts CLI | `npm run alerts:cli` |
[CLAUDE] | MCP server | `npm run mcp:server` |
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] === END FILE ===
