[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] # Admin Panel
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Access Control
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] All admin API routes call `requireAdminUser` from `auth-service.ts`. Non-admin requests receive 401/403.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] The admin nav is rendered by `src/app/(authenticated)/admin/admin-nav.tsx`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Admin Surfaces
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### User Management
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/users` — list QA users
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/users` — create QA user (name, email, temporaryPassword)
[CLAUDE] - `POST /api/admin/users/[id]/deactivate` — deactivate a user
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Implemented via `user-service.ts` (`listQaUsers`, `createQaUser`, `deactivateQaUser`).
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### Project Management
[CLAUDE] - `GET|POST /api/admin/projects` — list / create projects
[CLAUDE] - `PATCH /api/admin/projects/[id]` — update project (name, key, description, isArchived)
[CLAUDE] - `GET|POST /api/admin/projects/[id]/sections` — list / create sections
[CLAUDE] - `PATCH /api/admin/projects/[id]/sections/[sid]` — update section
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### Organizations View
[CLAUDE] - `GET /api/admin/organizations-with-projects` — flat join of all orgs and their projects (for admin overview)
