[CLAUDE] ### Monitoring
[CLAUDE] See [Monitoring](./monitoring.md) for full details. Admin dashboard summary at `GET /api/admin/dashboard/summary`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### Notifications Admin
