[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ### Bug Data Management
[CLAUDE] Admins can import and export bug data as batch jobs. See [Bugs — Import/Export](./bugs.md#data-import--export).
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Admin UI in `src/app/(authenticated)/admin/bug-data/`.
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Filter Components
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Admin sections with filterable lists use local filter state objects:
[CLAUDE] - `MonitoringAlertFilterState` — `alert-list-filters.ts`
[CLAUDE] - `NotificationDeliveryFilterState` — `notification-center-filters.ts`
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Both build `URLSearchParams` and validate before making API calls.
