[CLAUDE] - Date range validation for alert filters does not enforce ordering
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] ## Recommendation
[CLAUDE] 
[CLAUDE] Audit each function body against its test file (where present) to restore intended behavior. The type signatures and surrounding logic are sound — only the implementation bodies need filling in.
